Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:30.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}當你支撐著我的背後時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}你的溫柔就透過手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:37.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}傳達了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:41.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}雖然看不見的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:45.23,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}彷彿要折斷一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:50.03,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}但明天應該還是能飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:57.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}sunlight 如同太陽般的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:22:05.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}將那個名字用愛來呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:09.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(300,240)}吶 one's llight 那大量的愛
